               <scopecontent id="aspace_28a5c0efdd403e5fb22bfbb01f6a40ae">
                  <head>Scope and Contents</head>
                  <p>Includes incoming correspondence from Rosamund Grosvenor, Vita's mother Lady Sackville, Miss Macmillan, Hilda Matheson, and others. Outgoing correspondence includes letters from Vita to Lady Sackville and others, as well as copies of letters to Rosamund Grosvenor. Also includes correspondence documenting the sale of furniture.</p>
               </scopecontent>
            </c>
