                  <head>Scope and Contents</head>
                  <p>Includes correspondence from Pat Dansey, Sybil Colefax, Cyril Connolly, Ruth Draper, Rosamund Grosvenor, Eardley Knollys, Lord Lascelles, and others.</p>
               </scopecontent>
            </c>
            <c id="ref17" level="file">
