                  <head>Scope and Contents</head>
                  <p>Includes correspondence from Harold Nicolson, Benedict Nicolson, Nigel Nicolson, Lady Powerscourt, Lady Sackville, Lord (Lionel) Sackville, Gwen St. Aubyn, Christopher St. John, and others, including letters to Vita Sackville-West regarding her mother Lady Sackville. Also includes letters to Lady Sackville from Geoffrey Scott and Lord Sackville.</p>
               </scopecontent>
            </c>
            <c id="ref19" level="file">
               <did>
