                             label="Mixed Materials"
                             localtype="box">4</container>
               </did>
               <scopecontent id="aspace_689c2f63e8a7f01a9246932f1fb53b0d">
                  <head>Scope and Contents</head>
                  <p>Includes correspondence to Vita Sackville-West from Margaret Voigt, Mrs. Wilton, Laura James, the staff of the Queen Mother, and others, as well as assorted family correspondence, including condolence letters following the death of Lord Sackville. Also includes photographs of Hilda Matheson, excerpts from correspondence with Margaret Howard, and Nigel Nicolson correspondence and other papers related to his biographical writings.</p>
               </scopecontent>
